@startuml
actor Patient
entity "Clinic System" as CS
actor Doctor
actor "Admin Staff" as Admin

Patient -> CS: Select date
CS -> Patient: Return doctor roster
Patient -> CS: Select doctor
CS -> Patient: Return available slots
Patient -> CS: Select slot and type
CS -> Patient: Confirm appointment (Pending Review)
Doctor -> CS: View queue
CS -> Doctor: Show appointments
Doctor -> CS: Review appointment with note
CS -> Doctor: Confirm/Cancel
Patient -> CS: Request reschedule
CS -> Patient: New slot selection
Patient -> CS: Submit new slot
CS -> Patient: Updated appointment
Admin -> CS: View all queues
Admin -> CS: Review/reschedule any
@enduml
